<LP>
   ACTION INDUSTRIES Inc. (Pittsburgh) -- R. Craig Kirsch,
president and chief operating officer of this maker and
importer of household and hardware items, will assume the
additional post of chief executive officer, effective July
31, succeeding Ernest S. Berez, 64 years old, who will remain
chairman.
